  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> YoRHa Clan, <em><strong>S</strong></em> Designation, Level 12+ <br />You've uncovered more secrets of the world than you would've imagined to be possible. You attempt to use this knowledge in the battle for your existence, never telling others to preserve their happiness. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>You triple the range of all special forms of sight you possess.</li><li>You automatically succeed Insight checks to discern a creature's intentions towards you, having seen their behavioral patterns in the databanks of times long past.</li><li>Once per turn, when making a Perception or Insight check, you gain a bonus equal to 1/4th of your level.</li><li>If you would succeed a Read the Enemy check against a hostile creature, you immediately become aware of three values between their AC, current Hit Points, current Chakra points, their highest or lowest save bonus, and the amount of Tenacity Die they have remaining, if any. You may do this a number of times per long rest equal to half your proficiency bonus rounded up.</li></ul>",
